<lb n="0083c13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0083c1301">若有自書寫。教人書寫是無量壽宗要經。受
<lb n="0083c14" ed="T"/>持讀誦。當命終時。有九<note n="0083007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">十＋（九）【甲】</note><note n="0083007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">十【大】，十九【甲】</note><app n="0083007"><lem wit="【大】">十</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">十九</rdg></app>姟佛。現其人前。
<lb n="0083c15" ed="T"/>蒙<note n="0083008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（千）＋佛【甲】</note><note n="0083008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛【大】，千佛【甲】</note><app n="0083008"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">千佛</rdg></app>授手。能遊一切佛剎。莫於此經生於疑
<lb n="0083c16" ed="T"/>惑。陀羅尼曰。</p>
