<lb n="0084a09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0084a0901">若有方所自書<note n="0084002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔寫〕－【甲】＊</note><note n="0084002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寫【大】＊，〔－〕【甲】＊</note><app n="0084002"><lem wit="【大】">寫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。使人書<app type="star" corresp="#0084002"><lem wit="【大】">寫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>是無量壽經
<lb n="0084a10" ed="T"/>典之處。則為是塔皆應恭敬作禮。若是畜生。
<lb n="0084a11" ed="T"/>或<note n="0084003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">是＝為【甲】</note><note n="0084003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是【大】，為【甲】</note><app n="0084003"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">為</rdg></app>鳥獸得<note n="0084004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔聞〕－【甲】</note><note n="0084004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聞【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0084004"><lem wit="【大】">聞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>是經。如是等類。皆當不久
<lb n="0084a12" ed="T"/>得成<note n="0084005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一切〕－【甲】</note><note n="0084005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一切【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0084005"><lem wit="【大】">一切</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>種智。陀羅尼曰。</p>
