<lb n="0084a18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0084a1801">若有於是無量壽經自書寫若使人書<app type="star" corresp="#0084002"><lem wit="【大】">寫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。畢
<lb n="0084a19" ed="T"/>竟不受女人之身。陀羅尼曰。</p>
