<lb n="0084b29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0084b2901">如<note n="0084007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">四＝是【甲】</note><note n="0084007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">四【大】，是【甲】</note><app n="0084007"><lem wit="【大】">四</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">是</rdg></app>大海水可知滴數。是無量壽經典所生
<pb n="0084c" xml:id="T19.0936.0084c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0084c01" ed="T"/>果報。不可數量。陀羅尼曰。</p>
