<lb n="0084c07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0084c0701">若有自<note n="0084008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">書＋（寫）【甲】</note><note n="0084008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">書【大】，書寫【甲】</note><app n="0084008"><lem wit="【大】">書</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">書寫</rdg></app>。使人書寫。是無量壽經<note n="0084009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔典〕－【甲】</note><note n="0084009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">典【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0084009"><lem wit="【大】">典</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。又能
<lb n="0084c08" ed="T"/>護持供養。即如恭敬供養。一切十方佛土如
<lb n="0084c09" ed="T"/>來無有別異。陀羅尼曰。</p>
