<lb n="0084c27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0084c2701">爾時如來。說是經已。一切世間天人阿修羅
<lb n="0084c28" ed="T"/><note n="0084010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">揵＝健【甲】</note><note n="0084010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">揵【大】，健【甲】</note><app n="0084010"><lem wit="【大】">揵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">健</rdg></app>闥婆等。聞佛所說。皆大歡喜。信受奉行。</p></cb:div>
